article.headline: Long Island U. 74, Monmouth, N.J. 57
article.story: NEW YORK -- Jaytornah Wisseh scored 16 points and Julian Boyd added 15 points to Long Island University to a 74-57 victory against Monmouth, N.J., on Thursday night. Kyle Johnonas added 13 points and Arnold Mayorga had 10 for the Blackbirds (12-12, 8-5 Northeast), who were up 30-23 at halftime. Will Campbell scored 15 points to lead the Hawks (6-20, 4-9). Dutch Gaitley added 11 points. Travis Taylor's layup gave Monmouth a 21-18 lead ay 7:12 of the first half. LIU responded with a 12-2 run to close the half, highlighted by Boyd's dunk and a jumper.
